subject: Olympic Games (2008)
Shooting (Sport)
Paralympic Games
lead_paragraph: Sandra Fong, a member of the U.S. shooting team, and her sister, Danielle, a member of the paralympic shooting team, caught the eye of swimmer Dara Torres at a young age.
